HEADWORD: Quarterpace
<hw>Quar"ter*pace`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Arch.)</fld>
<def>A platform of a staircase where the stair turns at a right angle
only. See <er>Halfpace</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

